This directory contains a vendored, locally-patched copy of brush-builtins from
the brush shell project (https://github.com/reubeno/brush), used under the MIT
License. It is wired into the workspace via `[patch.crates-io]` so these
modifications can be maintained against the published release (brush-builtins
0.2.0).

  Copyright (c) 2024 reuben olinsky

Local modifications include: implementing previously-stubbed builtins, the
`wait` builtin (PID targeting plus the `-f`/`-n`/`-p` flags), and cancellation
support for the `read` builtin via poll. The remaining logic tracks upstream so
behavior matches the published crate.

